text: "Jeopardy!" host Alex Trebek clarifies a statement from his recent memoir about forgoing his cancer treatment if it stopped working: “That quote from the book was written BEFORE my current regimen, and I was going through some bad times." https://t.co/5OCjtlk9W4

name: NBCNews
text: NEW: For the first time in 30 years, Walmart, the nation's largest retailer, has announced it will be closed on Thanksgiving Day, saying it wants to give a break to essential staff who have been working during the pandemic. https://t.co/hdbrpWSAv4
